  "text": "where q(d) is the word that d is quantized to. To reduce quantization error and quantize similar features to the same words, we choose soft assignment similar with [CITATION_1] where a color descriptor is quantized as a combination of several words obtained by the nearest neighbor method. Quantization weighting is updated as:",
